      "situation": "quarter-end or year-end requires actuarial certification that loss reserves are adequate within stated confidence interval",
      "motivation": "ensure statutory and GAAP reserve adequacy, prevent regulator intervention, and provide accurate financial statements",
      "outcome": "actuarial reserve opinion issued and signed, reserve adjustments booked, financial statements certified",
      "success_criteria": [
